data.description: Charming home with unlimited possibilities! This cozy two bed, two bath home features some recent updates, including fresh paint, newer flooring and backsplash in the kitchen and new carpeting. Embrace the opportunity to add your personal touch and make it your own. Whether purchasing your first starter home, or looking for the perfect investment property, this home is a great opportunity! Conveniently located near shopping, schools and parks, this house is priced to sell. Don't miss the chance to bring your vision to life with this home!
